E hiwere Ministri Na-ahụ Maka Ihe Ndị Na-eme n'Ụlọ nke Lagos n'afọ 1979, Ministri a na-ahụ maka Ihe Ndị Na'Ụlọ agafeela ọtụtụ usoro mmepe na mgbanwe, ma n'ihe gbasara aha na ibu ọrụ
E guzobere Ministry of Home Affairs, Lottery, and Pools Betting n'okpuru ọchịchị Gọvanọ Lateef Jakande.
Mike Akhigbe, a gbanwere Ọfịs ahụ ka ọ bụrụ Ministri of Home Affairs na Tourism zuru oke, na Maazị Franklin Adejuwon dị ka Kọmishọna Ukwu na Maazọ Musuliu Obanikoro dị ka Kọmishọna ukwu nke Abụọ.

Maazị Akinwunmi Ambode, onye bụbu gọvanọ nke steeti Lagos, gbanwere aha ya ka ọ bụrụ Ministry of Home Affairs na 2015, ma nyefee Ministry of Tourism, Arts and Culture, and Special Duties na Ministry of Tourism, Art and Culture, na Special Duties, n'otu n'otu.
